snippet.title: Identity V - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Identity V, an asymmetrical horror mobile game developed by NetEase,  is now released on both Google Play Store and App Store.

________________________________________________________________________
Identity V is an asymmetrical horror mobile game developed by NetEase. 

For more information, visit the links below: 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/IdentityV/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/GameIdentityV
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/identityv/
